Plot: After failing to get his wife pregnant, a guy (Schneider) recruits his pals to steal the deposit he left at a sperm bank years ago.
Title: The Babymakers
Actors: Paul Schneider, Olivia Munn, Michael Yurchak, Wood Harris
tomatoConsensus: The Babymakers mistakes raunch for humor and, despite a few sporadic laughs, wastes its otherwise capable cast on gross-out gags and misfired one-liners.
